Show HN: a anonymous chat app unlike any other. 

Embedded video, live views, threading, and temporary identities without logging in. 

I'm Everyone is a realtime anonymous chat platform.

Current features are:
- Live realtime chat
- A fourchan plugin that adds sample content from /b to the feed until I get some actual users.

Start imeveryone.py and connect to localhost:8888 for example.


